OL,3,CThe Trapped: Daniel Hewitt exposes the
OL,4,CUK's dirty secret in new podcast series
OL,6,FITV News launches The Trapped - an
OL,7,Feight-part podcast exploring Daniel
OL,8,FHewitt's award-winning investigation
OL,9,Finto the state of housing in the UK.
OL,11,FSince 2021 Daniel has been travelling
OL,12,Fthe country speaking to people living
OL,13,Fin the worst conditions imaginable.
OL,15,FHere he recounts how a visit to a
OL,16,Fsingle block of flats in March of that
OL,17,Fyear led to a news report that exposed
OL,18,Fa national scandal - one that is still
OL,19,Fgoing on to this day.
