OL,3,CThe Trapped: Daniel Hewitt exposes the
OL,4,CUK's dirty secret in new podcast series
OL,6,FHave you heard The Trapped? Listen as
OL,7,FDaniel Hewitt exposes the UK's dirty
OL,8,Fsecret..
OL,10,FThere are few moments in life you can
OL,11,Fremember vividly, with genuine
OL,12,Fclarity. I can recall almost every
OL,13,Fminute of the time I spent inside the
OL,14,Fflats on Regina Road, Croydon.
OL,16,FOn a cold, spring morning I pulled up
OL,17,Fin my car and stared up at this tower
OL,18,Fblock, covered in cream-coloured
OL,19,Fcladding, piercing the south London
OL,20,Fskyline. The outside gave no hint of
OL,21,Fthe horrors inside.
