OL,6,FStepping into flat number 7, my feet
OL,7,Finstantly unsteady on the soaking wet
OL,8,Ffloor, the dank, sour smell hit me
OL,9,Flike a brick wall, my eyes could
OL,10,Fbarely register what they were seeing.
OL,12,FI had arrived to meet Fransoy, a
OL,13,Fmother-of-two who had reached out
OL,14,Fthrough a friend to our producer Sarah
OL,15,FO'Connell. Sarah and I had been
OL,16,Fworking together on a story about poor
OL,17,Fhousing conditions. It was early 2021,
OL,18,Fcoronavirus was spreading again and
OL,19,Flockdown measures had been
OL,20,Freintroduced.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
