OL,6,FI was a political correspondent at the
OL,7,Ftime, but I was desperate to get out
OL,8,Fof Westminster and around the country,
OL,9,Fto see what impact the pandemic was
OL,10,Fhaving on different people. I had seen
OL,11,FFacebook groups popping up of
OL,12,Ffrustrated social housing tenants
OL,13,Fposting pictures of mould, damp and
OL,14,Fdisrepair they said their landlords
OL,15,Fwere not fixing, blaming the pandemic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
