OL,6,FI had been sent a short video of
OL,7,FFransoy's flat - it looked bad and so
OL,8,Fwe decided to go down to see her with
OL,9,Fmy cameraman Ted. The video had given
OL,10,Fa small glimpse of the poor conditions
OL,11,Fshe and her boys were living in, but
OL,12,Fit was the tip of the iceberg. It was
OL,13,Fclear to me instantly, as I watched
OL,14,Fwater cascade down black walls covered
OL,15,Fin furry mould, that this was
OL,16,Fdangerous housing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
