OL,4,CUK's dirty secret in new podcast series
OL,6,FAs a reporter, you usually know
OL,7,Finstinctively when you have a strong
OL,8,Fstory. I was utterly convinced that
OL,9,Fwhat we had found in that tower block
OL,10,Fneeded to be shared with the widest
OL,11,Faudience possible. This was not a
OL,12,Fstory about bad housing conditions in
OL,13,Fa flat in south London - it felt so
OL,14,Fmuch bigger than that.
OL,16,FI felt more angry than I have ever
OL,17,Ffelt in my life. How had these
OL,18,Ffamilies been left to live like this
OL,19,Ffor months? Why were their complaints
OL,20,Fbeing ignored? Who was to blame? When
OL,21,Fdid people stop caring?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
