OL,3,CThe Trapped: Daniel Hewitt exposes the
OL,4,CUK's dirty secret in new podcast series
OL,6,FThe Trapped is the story of the
OL,7,Fjourney we have been on to answer
OL,8,Fthose questions.
OL,10,FThe day after airing our TV report on
OL,11,FITV News, the floodgates opened.
OL,12,FEmails and messages from social
OL,13,Fhousing tenants from across the
OL,14,Fcountry kept coming and coming, so
OL,15,Fmuch so that we set up a dedicated
OL,16,Fhousing email address -
OL,17,Fhousingstories@itv.com. Nearly four
OL,18,Fyears on, that inbox is still going,
OL,19,Fstill being used by tenants contacting
OL,20,Fus about their housing situations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
