OL,6,FThe Trapped is the culmination of many
OL,7,Fyears of investigative reporting that
OL,8,Fwould simply not have been possible
OL,9,Fwithout the bravery and courage of the
OL,10,Fpeople left to rot in Britain's broken
OL,11,Fhousing system who have been willing
OL,12,Fto speak out and trust us with their
OL,13,Fstories.
