OL,4,CUK's dirty secret in new podcast series
OL,6,FIn the series, you will hear one
OL,7,Fcouncil leader say it is wrong that
OL,8,Ftenants felt compelled to come to us,
OL,9,FITV News, instead of them, their
OL,10,Flandlord. But they did go to them -
OL,11,Ftime and time and time again tenants
OL,12,Freport problems to councils and
OL,13,Fhousing associations and landlords who
OL,14,Fare willing to take their rent, but
OL,15,Funwilling or incapable of carrying out
OL,16,Fbasic repairs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
