OL,3,CThe Trapped: Daniel Hewitt exposes the
OL,4,CUK's dirty secret in new podcast series
OL,6,FBecause the housing crisis is
OL,7,Fultimately about power - who has it
OL,8,Fand who doesn't. The state has
OL,9,Fretreated too far from its basic
OL,10,Fobligation to house its citizens in
OL,11,Fdecent, affordable homes. The Trapped
OL,12,Flays bare the heartbreaking
OL,13,Fconsequences ` and the changes that
OL,14,Fare needed.
OL,16,FThe journey continues.
OL,18,FHead to www.thetrapped.co.uk to hear
OL,19,Fthe full series and see the visuals
OL,20,Fthat support each episode.
